<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire is probably infrequent in this alliance since stands are relatively open and have low fuel loads. <i>Mortonia utahensis </i>does not appear to sprout after fire in California, and fire in the rocky, open stands is probably very rare.</div>
